data.description: Beautiful Two Story Home in West Lancaster! This charming 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom home, built in 1992, offers a versatile floor plan, with a full bedroom and bathroom downstairs. It has a family room with a cozy fireplace perfect for the holidays and a covered patio for those summer days in the AV. The mature landscaping and RV access make this property a dream for outdoor enthusiasts. Plus, its prime location near shops, which  means you'll have everything you need right at your doorstep. Don't miss out on the chance to call this lovely West Lancaster property your own - seize this perfect opportunity for first-time homebuyers! Call us for your appointment today!
